Marisol Nichols https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marisol_Nichols 0 Marisol Nichols (born November 2, 1973) is an American actress. She is best known for her role in the sixth season of 24 as Special Agent Nadia Yassir and as Hermione Lodge in the 2017 thriller series Riverdale.
